BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Macbeth
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261003T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261003T214500
DTSTAMP:20260707T014648Z
UID:occ-1462@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Shakespeare's Scottish tragedy of witches\, prophecy\, and a c
 ouple who won't wait for fate\, from the Atlanta Shakespeare Company.\n\nT
 hree witches hail a victorious Scottish general as a future king\, and he 
 and his wife decide not to leave the crown to chance. Shakespeare's shorte
 st tragedy traces their climb from prophecy to murder to guilt that will n
 ot wash off. From the Atlanta Shakespeare Company\, performed with food an
 d drink served at your table. A 2025 Suzi Bass Awards Recommended Show.
GEO:33.768171;-84.3851523
LAST-MODIFIED:20260707T013014Z
LOCATION:Shakespeare Tavern Playhouse\, 499 Peachtree St NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
